 Artemis reminds both mortals and heroes that the wilderness is sacred—and that those who forget the gods do so at their peril.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->',	'The Calydonian Boar: Artemis Unleashes the Wild',	'',	'inherit',	'closed',	'closed',	'',	'20-revision-v1',	'',	'',	'2025-04-25 16:24:19',	'2025-04-25 16:24:19',	'',	20,	'http://localhost:10034/?p=22',	0,	'revision',	'',	0),
